    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q: What is the difference between your Lightweight Blanket and Weighted Blanket?</p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">A: The difference between our two blankets is simple: One provides additional weighted comfort using 1mm glass beads (Weighted Blanket) and the other provides light comfort with no additional weight (Lightweight Blanket).</p>
    
    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q: Is your Lightweight Blanket wrinkle resistant?</p>
