    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q: What is ClimaSense?</p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">A: ClimaSense™ is powered by 37.5® Technology which uses naturally derived minerals that adjust to your body’s need for cooling or warmth, helping to regulate your temperature while you sleep. </p>
    
    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q: What is 37.5® Technology?</p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">A: 37.5 Technology is triggered by humidity. Humidity in your microclimate is the gauge for whether you are hot or cold. When you’re hot, the active minerals embedded within your comforter use your body’s energy to remove moisture, helping to cool you down. When you’re cold, the same active minerals use your body’s energy to help keep you warm. </p>
    
    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q: Why is it called 37.5®?</p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">A: It’s called 37.5® Technology because it helps keep your body at the ideal core temperature of 37.5˚ Celsius during exercise, and helps keep the microclimate next to your skin while sleeping at the ideal relative humidity of 37.5%.</p>    
    
    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q: Can I use this comforter year-round?</p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">A:  YES! Our comforter can transition easily for any season. Simply layer your comforter with other bedding pieces appropriate for each season to tailor your bed to your sleep preferences. </p>    
    
    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q: Can I wash the comforter at home?</p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">A: To keep your ClimaSense comforter in the very best condition, we DO NOT recommend machine washing.  The delicate Baffle Box construction will become damaged with agitation and the down alternative fibers may clump in the wash. </p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">Dry cleaning or spot cleaning is highly recommended; small spots may be removed by using warm water and soft soap like Woolite. Do not bleach. Do not iron. </p>
    
    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q: Can I add a duvet cover? </p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">A:  We encourage using a duvet cover to help keep your ClimaSense Comforter clean and looking its best. The protective layer of a duvet cover can help keep body oils, skin cells, and more from getting in your comforter.  View our available Duvet Covers <a class="faq__link" href="https://luxome.com/products/duvet-cover?variant=40040987557949">HERE</a>.</p>
    
    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q: How many loops does the comforter have? </p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">A: The ClimaSense comforter has 8 loops — one on each corner and one on the middle of each of the four sides. This is 2x as many as standard comforters and will help keep your comforter in place and avoid bunching with use.</p>
    
    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q: If I add a duvet cover, will the 37.5® Technology still work?</p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">A: Adding a duvet cover will not stop the effectiveness of the 37.5® Technology minerals.</p>    
    
    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q:  Can I use one of your minky or bamboo weighted blanket removable covers for my comforter?</p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">A: No. Our removable covers are made specifically for the size and specifications of our weighted blankets. Choose one of our <a class="faq__link" href="https://luxome.com/products/duvet-cover?variant=40040987557949">Duvet Cover</a> options, which are specially designed for the ClimaSense Comforter.</p>

    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q: What is a Baffle Box?</p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">A: Baffle Box construction features internal fabric walls that separate the top and bottom layers of fabric to offer exceptional loft and distribution of fill.  This is one of the reasons our comforter is so fluffy! </p>
    
    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q: Is the ClimaSense Comforter cool to the touch? </p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">A: ClimaSense is not cool to the touch. The active particles in 37.5® Technology work on a microscopic level to remove moisture and help maintain your core body temperature, allowing you to sleep with less temperature-induced disruption. </p>
    
    <p class="faq-q-bold">Q: Will your technology wash out?  </p>
    <p class="faq-a-normal">A: The active volcanic minerals in the 37.5® Technology are naturally derived and sustainably harvested volcanic minerals that are chemical-free and will not wash out. </p>
